index.html.title: HueColor
index.html.name: HueColor
index.html.summary: Color library for development with Philips Hue

HueColor.html.title: HueColor
HueColor.html.name: HueColor
HueColor.html.description: Contains color information and methods to work with them. Do not construct this directly, use the static factory functions.

HueColor.html#.fromRgb.title: <static> fromRgb( red, green, blue )  {HueColor}
HueColor.html#.fromRgb.name: fromRgb
HueColor.html#.fromRgb.description: Constructs a new Color given red, green, and blue.

HueColor.html#.fromCIE.title: <static> fromCIE( x, y, brightness )  {HueColor}
HueColor.html#.fromCIE.name: fromCIE
HueColor.html#.fromCIE.description: Constructs a new Color given a CIE point and brightness.

HueColor.html#.fromHex.title: <static> fromHex( hex )  {HueColor}
HueColor.html#.fromHex.name: fromHex
HueColor.html#.fromHex.description: Constructs a new Color given a CSS-style hex code.

HueColor.html#.fromHsb.title: <static> fromHsb( hue, saturation, brightness )  {HueColor}
HueColor.html#.fromHsb.name: fromHsb
HueColor.html#.fromHsb.description: Constructs a new Color given HSB values.

HueColor.html#toRgb.title: toRgb()  {Array.<number>}
HueColor.html#toRgb.name: toRgb
HueColor.html#toRgb.description: Converts the color to RGB. Note that the CIE-to-RGB conversion is necessarily approximate.

HueColor.html#toHex.title: toHex()  {string}
HueColor.html#toHex.name: toHex
HueColor.html#toHex.description: Converts the color to a CSS-style hex string. Note that the CIE-to-RGB conversion is necessarily approximate.

HueColor.html#toCie.title: toCie()  {Array.<number>}
HueColor.html#toCie.name: toCie
HueColor.html#toCie.description: Converts the color to a CIE color that Hue lamps are capable of showing. Note that the RGB-to-CIE conversion is necessarily approximate.
